WEBVTT

1
01:15:54.900 --> 01:15:57.770 
(2又2分之1狐狸周)

2
01:15:54.900 --> 01:15:57.770 
三天后

3
01:15:59.510 --> 01:16:02.510 
这三位在我个人看来非常执着的农场主
These three, in this reporter's opinion, obsessed farmers

4
01:16:02.600 --> 01:16:04.260 
依然深信相关狐狸
remain convinced the fox in question

5
01:16:04.260 --> 01:16:07.180 
最终会现身 为什么呢
will eventually reappear. Why?

6
01:16:07.430 --> 01:16:09.160 
狐狸生来就不会住下水道里
Foxes aren't meant to live in a sewer.

7
01:16:09.160 --> 01:16:09.730 
他们在避难
They're refugees.

8
01:16:09.810 --> 01:16:11.600 
他们在那下面只能吃
All they have to eat down there is...

9
01:16:11.690 --> 01:16:12.810 
垃圾
Trash!

10
01:16:13.190 --> 01:16:14.860 
而且并没有多少
And not much of it.

11
01:16:15.190 --> 01:16:16.230 
好的
Uh-huh.

12
01:16:16.320 --> 01:16:17.320 
谢谢农场主们
Thank you, farmers.

13
01:16:17.320 --> 01:16:20.610 
行动台12频道 Dan Peabody为您报道
For Action 12, this is Dan Peabody.

14
01:16:23.030 --> 01:16:24.160 
现在什么情况
What are we looking at?

